description: Tsubaki, often referred to as Okami by http://anidb.net/ch90640 [Kiri], is the owner of Konohanatei. She was the one that http://anidb.net/ch90639 [Yuzu] got entrusted to by http://anidb.net/ch91585 [Yao Bikuni]. Even though she might appear that way, she`s kind and caring towards her employees, especially noticeable when she threatened one guest to leave the Konohanatai because he was molesting http://anidb.net/ch90644 [Ren].
name: Tsubaki
